<p>Greetings,</p>

<p>I hope you all had a great fall break! This is your October/mid-semester Libraries announcement!</p>

<p>Reaching your librarian, Chasz Griego:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Email: cgriego@andrew.cmu.edu</li>
  <li>Schedule an <a href="https://cmu.libcal.com/appointments/cgriego">appointment</a></li>
